 ### Use CollectionsMarshal.GetValueRefOrNullRef for Lookup-and-Update
 🟡 **DO** use `CollectionsMarshal.GetValueRefOrAddDefault` for dictionary update patterns | .NET 6+

 ❌
 ```csharp
